# GENEVE (RFC 8926) over UDP/IPv4 port 6081, protocol type 0x6558 (Transparent Ethernet Bridging),
# VNI 100, no options — tunneling a complete inner Ethernet frame (eth/ipv4/icmp echo-request).
# source: standard GENEVE header + a real inner eth frame, sent via a real UDP socket to 127.0.0.1:6081
# on a debian:12 container's ethernet lo, captured with tcpdump. Inner recurses via EthernetII (which
# already accepts a 'geneve' tunnel parent), like VXLAN.
